{"tid":1226042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尋日既媽媽遊行，我俾左我老母睇","createTime":"2019-06-15T09:29:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T10:05:55.000Z","uid":130695,"like":96,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"511a73d1f9986487f14879c1b0ff0a3b20e512b5","tid":1226042,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:29:22.000Z","msg":"之前佢一直唔明點解我咁反修例<br />\n9/6既時候，佢夢到我係街度訓<br />\n12/6既時候，佢仲夢到我係前線<br />\n返黎仲問我，點解仲要出去<br />\n出面好似打仗咁，有人拆磚警察又開槍<br />\n我將我見到既慢慢同佢講清楚<br />\n14/6，六千個媽媽出黎遊行<br />\n當日影片既媽媽都出左黎<br />\n我行過聽到佢係度睇，仲喊緊<br />\n15/6，林鄭出完記者會<br />\n我老母好嬲，問我 聽日幾點遊行<br />\n佢年紀唔細，講緊七十幾歲<br />\n我剩係想問話返工不了，好熱不了既人<br />\n你地睇左咁多日，加埋今日淋病咁既態度咁既回應<br />\n屌佢老母閪，點樣收貨?<br />\n16/6 不見不散<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">認清目標，撤修例，放義士！</span></strong></span><br />\n槍口對外，兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n不分化，不篤灰，不割蓆<br />\n拒絕假消息，封鎖假輿論<br />\n自己香港自己救<br />\n撤修例放義士"},{"pid":"1f6e93e0e9150ae7b9a60170f5ef301c8b798b1b","tid":1226042,"uid":130695,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:43:36.000Z","msg":"唔該你，同身邊每個人講<br />\n聽日，唔理你各行各業，和理勇武<br />\n只需要將你人生中既一日空出黎<br />\n我地香港人，我地愛香港"},{"pid":"79fa017cc87db7cb29b879db301fd1f53f28ff46","tid":1226042,"uid":19278,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:50:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v1NCBu7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv1NCBu7.jpg&h=a47768e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e34868cb041541e13f9e2d327869ef33dd98ee7","tid":1226042,"uid":245126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:51:52.000Z","msg":"多謝姨姨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4c5628b2879cae8ab75ab518b0ea0b1c7ff37e","tid":1226042,"uid":104086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:52:42.000Z","msg":"振興香港消費！全城戶外運動裝備及須知<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1224572\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1224572</a>"},{"pid":"e788c0cf797ea3d4731ab09e6d33137e93cc5a9c","tid":1226042,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:54:33.000Z","msg":"[輔導/心理學界都憤怒] 切勿亂用同理心(Empathy)一詞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1226025\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1226025</a>"},{"pid":"ef70bf2532c4addd39ef6c2b2034977d013b2136","tid":1226042,"uid":104446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79fa017cc87db7cb29b879db301fd1f53f28ff46","tid":1226042,"uid":19278,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:50:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v1NCBu7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv1NCBu7.jpg&h=a47768e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:58:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff1b044e1a1222af2f1e0484025aa96a10fb0a8","tid":1226042,"uid":32140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:58:55.000Z","msg":"聽日需要每一個香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去同呢個漠視民意嘅政府講，要佢撤回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10096cab67dc000080c75691663f54abef345f5a","tid":1226042,"uid":259302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T10:04:53.000Z","msg":"1.撤回修例<br />\n2.收回示威是暴動的定性<br />\n3.釋放所有過去一週因示威被捕的人<br />\n4.追究警方使用過份武力，甚至暴力<br />\n若明天和平遊行有人叫「林鄭下台」「打倒中共」「港獨」等無關上述四點的口號，請勿理會，現在要集中目標。"},{"pid":"16cd5a2a9cb2809ff8e6a3706686f6b0e3655132","tid":1226042,"uid":130695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"79fa017cc87db7cb29b879db301fd1f53f28ff46","tid":1226042,